<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/the-uss-wave-of-hospital-closures-left-us-ill-equipped-for-covid-19/">The USâ€™s Wave of Hospital Closures Left Us Ill-Equipped for COVID-19</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Since 1975, as the population grew by 115 million, the number of hospital beds shrank from 1.5 million to 925,000. </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/margaret-flowers/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Margaret Flowers</a></span>, </dd>
